Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.63,0:00:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,璘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.61,0:00:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望圣诞老人送你什么礼物啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.43,0:00:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.18,0:00:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没想好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.39,0:00:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点想好可就要来不及咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是从很远的地方来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,0:00:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来 说说现在最想要什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lop Ear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶? 那个不是有了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想要个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.07,0:01:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.24,0:01:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.48,0:01:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,璘儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.27,0:01:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.90,0:01:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞树
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.87,0:01:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...工作上用的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们把圣诞树立起来好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吉 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是装在树顶上的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.97,0:02:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家没有烟囱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.66,0:02:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞老人能进来的 安啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我把门锁打开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}致圣诞老人 感谢您的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那胡萝卜是干什么的啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给驯鹿的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要关灯咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞老人只会给睡着的孩子送礼物哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶? 那快点关灯!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想见圣诞老人一面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,璘 吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还要谢谢驯鹿


